headline: CAIA Association and Franklin Templeton Unite to Help Investment Professionals Deliver Better Client Outcomes and Expand Access to Global Networks
summary: ABU DHABI, United Arab Emirates, December 09, 2025--The Chartered Alternative Investment Analyst Association (CAIA), the global professional body for alternative investment professionals, has entered a multi-year strategic partnership with Franklin Templeton, a leading global institutional asset manager. This newly expanded collaboration, formalized during a signing ceremony at Abu Dhabi Finance Week, underscores a shared commitment to deepening education, community, and industry standards acros

headline: Custody Bank Q3 Earnings: Franklin Resources (NYSE:BEN) is the Best in the Biz
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at custody bank stocks, starting with Franklin Resources (NYSE:BEN).
